column5: Week 8 on Extreme Angler TV- on WFN (thursday, sat & sunday)  BRONZE & BUCKET BONANZA  First up, Scotty Murison smashes some late fall stickworm smallies hiding and feeding in shallow weedy largemouth water in tornado-like conditions in the Muskoka`s.  Then K-Dawg is hunting for cruising oversized bass on those small isolated weed patches everybody drives over with there boat- the action is fast and furious with a few pleasant surprises.  http://www.extremeanglertv.com  Extreme Army Team Spike
I know what week that was. We were chased of Geobay by twisters! Wasn't fun. My old gallery had picks of that day!
